  <brief_title>Effect of AQW051 in Patients With Memory Impairment</brief_title>
  <official_title>A 4-week, Parallel-group, Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled, Adaptive Proof of Concept Study of AQW051 at up to Three Dose Levels for the Treatment of Patients With Findings Consistent With Mild Alzheimer's Disease (AD) or Amnestic Mild Cognitive Impairment (Amnestic MCI)</official_title>
