  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will investigate AQW051 in patients with either mild Alzheimer's disease or
      amnestic mild cognitive impairment. The effect on cognitive impairment will be measure using
      validated computerized tests which measure cognitive function. This study will also explore
      the safety and tolerability of AQW051 in these patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
